{"tid":731484,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個最難搵廁所既商場","createTime":"2018-07-06T08:18:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-09T16:22:08.000Z","uid":7365,"like":46,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"8649415c8e70ffbd4752f524cb3e27bd74c3011b","tid":731484,"uid":7365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T08:18:38.000Z","msg":"岩岩行過中環置地廣場諗住去個廁所<br />\n點知行左10個鐘都冇一個指示牌寫住洗手間喺咩方向<br />\n仲整左幾部導航既機幫人搵唔同鋪頭<br />\n玩touch mon但係感應又慢 禁完廁所又要禁男女廁 禁都禁左半分鐘 仲要哂時間睇地圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後 終於見到有寫廁所既指示牌 指左個方向 屌 一望個廁所就喺眼前<br />\n係咪即係我要花10分鐘搵到呢個指示牌 我先搵到個廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有冇其他地方搵廁所都係咁難"},{"pid":"a6de5974f1223d9ee8c271a0a07b86455093f74a","tid":731484,"uid":91884,"like":11,"dislike":19,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T10:51:39.000Z","msg":"The one"},{"pid":"48238f4da3aac7b56ed1b6050eefef789f2a9916","tid":731484,"uid":37431,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T10:53:06.000Z","msg":"唔識問人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3259c171aea7a8e10cb61998240d67e4cf83f046","tid":731484,"uid":151865,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T10:55:44.000Z","msg":"路在口邊 出親街有咩都一定第一時間問人先"},{"pid":"2c0888c125c3426bf3c98f833ded3f6a615e9d9e","tid":731484,"uid":3,"like":17,"dislike":69,"score":-52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T10:57:31.000Z","msg":"圓方 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbfce8ff26fcb04ec13d52ae98ee7ff5b8629c96","tid":731484,"uid":20820,"like":39,"dislike":6,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T11:00:20.000Z","msg":"德福，剩係搵到女廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e388f2d63da8d5d724beb2a53d620f67e754080","tid":731484,"uid":26084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T11:49:20.000Z","msg":"家樂坊"},{"pid":"8119b3205669c852199c33fe3aa59dbe